 was quick. Petaloons is now my go-to brand.”<\/p>\n          <h4>Amit Deshmukh<\/h4>\n          <span>Nagpur<\/span>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"pet-review-card\">\n          <div class=\"pet-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n          <p>“Loved the tuxedo! It made our pet look like a star at the birthday party.”<\/p>\n          <h4>Neha Kapoor<\/h4>\n          <span>Delhi<\/span>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"pet-review-card\">\n          <div class=\"pet-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n          <p>“Very good quality and comfortable fitting. Worth buying for festive occasions.”<\/p>\n          <h4>Siddharth Iyer<\/h4>\n          <span>Bengaluru<\/span>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <!-- Duplicate cards for smooth infinite scroll -->\n\n        <div class=\"pet-review-card\">\n          <div class=\"pet-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n          <p>“Perfect fit and amazing quality! My dog looked so cute in the sherwani.”<\/p>\n          <h4>Priya Sharma<\/h4>\n          <span>Mumbai<\/span>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"pet-review-card\">\n          <div class=\"pet-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n          <p>“Fabric is soft and comfortable. My pug wore it for the full function without any issue.”<\/p>\n          <h4>Rahul Verma<\/h4>\n          <span>Nagpur<\/span>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"pet-review-card\">\n          <div class=\"pet-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n          <p>“The dog lehenga was beautiful. Stitching and finishing were much better than expected.”<\/p>\n          <h4>Anjali Mehta<\/h4>\n          <span>Pune<\/span>\n        <\/div>\n\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<style>\n.pet-reviews-section {\n  width: 100%;\n  padding: 70px 20px;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff8ef 0%, #ffffff 55%, #f2fbff 100%);\n  font-family: inherit;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-container {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: auto;\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-header {\n  text-align: center;\n  max-width: 760px;\n  margin: 0 auto 42px;\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-badge {\n  display: inline-block;\n  background: #ffe3bd;\n  color: #7a3d00;\n  padding: 10px 18px;\n  border-radius: 40px;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  font-weight: 800;\n  margin-bottom: 16px;\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-header h2 {\n  font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 50px);\n  line-height: 1.1;\n  color: #1f2933;\n  margin: 0 0 14px;\n  font-weight: 900;\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-header p {\n  color: #5f6c7b;\n  font-size: 17px;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-slider {\n  position: relative;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  padding: 10px 0;\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-slider::before,\n.pet-reviews-slider::after {\n  content: \"\";\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 0;\n  width: 90px;\n  height: 100%;\n  z-index: 2;\n  pointer-events: none;\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-slider::before {\n  left: 0;\n  background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff8ef, transparent);\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-slider::after {\n  right: 0;\n  background: linear-gradient(to left, #f2fbff, transparent);\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-track {\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 22px;\n  width: max-content;\n  animation: petReviewScroll 32s linear infinite;\n}\n\n.pet-reviews-slider:hover .pet-reviews-track {\n  animation-play-state: paused;\n}\n\n.pet-review-card {\n  width: 330px;\n  min-height: 250px;\n  background: #ffffff;\n  border-radius: 26px;\n  padding: 26px;\n  box-shadow: 0 16px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n  border: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n}\n\n.pet-stars {\n  color: #f7941d;\n  font-size: 20px;\n  letter-spacing: 2px;\n  margin-bottom: 14px;\n}\n\n.pet-review-card p {\n  color: #374151;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  line-height: 1.65;\n  margin: 0 0 22px;\n}\n\n.pet-review-card h4 {\n  color: #1f2933;\n  font-size: 17px;\n  margin: 0 0 4px;\n  font-weight: 900;\n}\n\n.pet-review-card span {\n  color: #7b8794;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n@keyframes petReviewScroll {\n  0% {\n    transform: translateX(0);\n  }\n  100% {\n    transform: translateX(